info:
Jika IP Node-RED berubah, jalankan SQL ini di Supabase SQL Editor:

  ALTER DATABASE postgres SET app.nodered_url = 'http://IP-BARU:1880';

Tidak perlu edit SQL migration lagi.

Jika Node-RED ada di cloud (mis. Railway, Render, DigitalOcean):
  ALTER DATABASE postgres SET app.nodered_url = 'https://domain-node-red.com';

Jika pakai ngrok untuk testing:
  ALTER DATABASE postgres SET app.nodered_url = 'https://xxxx.ngrok-free.app';
